511  [TargetedPatchingOptOut("Performance critical to inline across NGen image boundaries"), MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)]
512  public bool LeaveScope(bool bubbleReturnValue = false)
513  {
514 #if TRACE_SCOPE
515  _scopeTrace.Trace("Leave scope begin");
516 #endif
517 
518  if (CurrentScope.Parent == null)
519  {
520 #if TRACE_SCOPE
521  _scopeTrace.Trace("Internal error leaving scope, parent scope is null.");
522 #endif
523 
524  throw CreateInternalException(
525  "Internal error leaving scope, parent scope is null.");
526  }
527 
528  if (bubbleReturnValue)
529  {
530  var ret = GetReturnValue(true);
531  CurrentScope = CurrentScope.Parent;
532 
533  if (ret != null)
534  {
535  SetReturnValue(ret);
536 
537 #if TRACE_SCOPE
538  _scopeTrace.Trace("Leave scope end");
539 #endif
540 
541  return true;
542  }
543  }
544  else
545  {
546  CurrentScope = CurrentScope.Parent;
547  }
548 
549 #if TRACE_SCOPE
550  _scopeTrace.Trace("Leave scope end");
551 #endif
552 
553  return false;
554  }

660  [TargetedPatchingOptOut("Performance critical to inline across NGen image boundaries"), MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)]
661  private AphidObject InterpretEqualityExpression(BinaryOperatorExpression expression)
662  {
663  var left = (AphidObject)InterpretExpression(expression.LeftOperand);
664  var right = (AphidObject)InterpretExpression(expression.RightOperand);
665 
666  bool val;
667 
668  if (left == null)
669  {
670  throw CreateUndefinedMemberException(expression, expression.LeftOperand);
671  }
672  else if (right == null)
673  {
674  throw CreateUndefinedMemberException(expression, expression.RightOperand);
675  }
676  else
677  {
678  if (left.Value != null && right.Value != null)
679  {
680  Type leftType = left.Value.GetType(), rightType = right.Value.GetType();
681  val = InterpretEqualityExpression(left.Value, leftType, right.Value, rightType);
682  }
683  else if (left.Value != null)
684  {
685  val = left.Value.Equals(right.Value);
686  }
687  else if (right.Value != null)
688  {
689  val = right.Value.Equals(left.Value);
690  }
691  else
692  {
693  val = left.Count == 0 && right.Count == 0;
694  }
695  }
696 
697  if (expression.Operator == AphidTokenType.NotEqualOperator)
698  {
699  val = !val;
700  }
701 
702  return new AphidObject(val);
703  }

705  // Todo: add interop support for dynamic members e.g. Path.{'Combine'}
706  [TargetedPatchingOptOut("Performance critical to inline across NGen image boundaries"), MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)]
707  private AphidObject InterpretMemberInteropExpression(
708  object lhs,
709  BinaryOperatorExpression expression,
710  bool returnRef = false,
711  Func<AphidObject> dynamicHandler = null)
712  {
713  if (expression.RightOperand.Type != AphidExpressionType.IdentifierExpression)
714  {
715  throw CreateRuntimeException(
716  "Invalid member interop access, expected identifier on right-hand " +
717  "side of expression '{0}'.",
718  expression);
719  }
720 
721  MemberInfo[] members;
722 
723  if (lhs != null)
724  {
725  members = GetInteropInstanceMembers(lhs, expression);
726  }
727  else
728  {
729  var path = FlattenPath(expression);
730  var type = InteropTypeResolver.ResolveType(GetImports().ToArray(), path);
731  members = GetInteropStaticMembers(type, path);
732  TypeInfo nestedTypeInfo;
733 
734  if (members.Length == 1 &&
735  (nestedTypeInfo = members[0] as TypeInfo) != null)
736  {
737  return new AphidObject(nestedTypeInfo);
738  }
739  }
740 
741  return InterpretMemberInteropExpression(
742  lhs,
743  members,
744  expression,
745  returnRef,
746  dynamicHandler);
747  }

749  [TargetedPatchingOptOut("Performance critical to inline across NGen image boundaries"), MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)]
750  private AphidObject InterpretMemberInteropExpression(
751  object lhs,
752  MemberInfo[] members,
753  BinaryOperatorExpression expression,
754  bool returnRef = false,
755  Func<AphidObject> dynamicHandler = null)
756  {
757  if (members.Length == 1)
758  {
759  var propInfo = members[0] as PropertyInfo;
760 
761  if (propInfo != null)
762  {
763  if (!returnRef)
764  {
765  return propInfo.PropertyType != typeof(AphidObject) ?
766  new AphidObject(propInfo.GetValue(lhs)) :
767  (AphidObject)propInfo.GetValue(lhs);
768  }
769  else
770  {
771  return new AphidObject(new AphidInteropReference(lhs, propInfo));
772  }
773  }
774 
775  var fieldInfo = members[0] as FieldInfo;
776 
777  if (fieldInfo != null)
778  {
779  if (!returnRef)
780  {
781  return fieldInfo.FieldType != typeof(AphidObject) ?
782  new AphidObject(fieldInfo.GetValue(lhs)) :
783  (AphidObject)fieldInfo.GetValue(lhs);
784  }
785  else
786  {
787  return new AphidObject(new AphidInteropReference(lhs, fieldInfo));
788  }
789  }
790  }
791  else if (members.Length == 0)
792  {
793  if (dynamicHandler == null)
794  {
795  throw CreateRuntimeException(
796  "Could not find property '{0}'",
797  expression.RightOperand.ToIdentifier().ToIdentifier());
798  }
799  else
800  {
801  return dynamicHandler();
802  }
803  }
804 
805  return new AphidObject(new AphidInteropMember(expression, lhs, members));
806  }

850  [TargetedPatchingOptOut("Performance critical to inline across NGen image boundaries"), MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)]
851  private object InterpretMemberExpression(BinaryOperatorExpression expression, bool returnRef = false)
852  {
853  var obj = InterpretExpression(expression.LeftOperand) as AphidObject;
854 
855  Type type;
856 
857  if (obj != null && ((type = obj.Value as Type) != null))
858  {
859  var name = ((IdentifierExpression)expression.RightOperand).Identifier;
860 
861  if (!type.Assembly.IsDynamic)
862  {
863  var members = GetInteropStaticMembers(type, name);
864 
865  if (members.Length != 0)
866  {
867  var nestedType = members[0] as Type;
868 
869  return nestedType == null ?
870  InterpretMemberInteropExpression(
871  null,
872  members,
873  expression,
874  returnRef,
875  null) :
876  new AphidObject(nestedType);
877  }
878 
879  members = GetInteropInstanceMembers(type, name);
880 
881  if (members.Length != 0)
882  {
883  return InterpretMemberInteropExpression(
884  type,
885  members,
886  expression,
887  returnRef,
888  null);
889  }
890  }
891  else
892  {
893  var members = GetInteropInstanceMembers(type, name);
894 
895  if (members.Length != 0)
896  {
897  return InterpretMemberInteropExpression(
898  type,
899  members,
900  expression,
901  returnRef,
902  null);
903  }
904 
905  members = GetInteropStaticMembers(type, name);
906 
907  if (members.Length != 0)
908  {
909  var nestedType = members[0] as Type;
910 
911  return nestedType == null ?
912  InterpretMemberInteropExpression(
913  null,
914  members,
915  expression,
916  returnRef,
917  null) :
918  new AphidObject(nestedType);
919  }
920  }
921 
922  var ext = TypeExtender.TryResolve(
923  CurrentScope,
924  type,
925  key: ((IdentifierExpression)expression.RightOperand).Identifier,
926  isAphidType: false,
927  isCtor: false,
928  isDynamic: false,
929  returnRef: returnRef);
930 
931  if (ext != null)
932  {
933  return ext;
934  }
935  }
936 
937  if (expression.RightOperand.Type == AphidExpressionType.IdentifierExpression)
938  {
939  var interopMember = InteropMethodResolver.TryResolveMember(
940  expression,
941  obj,
942  returnRef);
943 
944  if (interopMember != null)
945  {
946  return interopMember;
947  }
948  }
949 
950  string key;
951 
952  if (expression.RightOperand is IdentifierExpression)
953  {
954  key = (expression.RightOperand as IdentifierExpression).Identifier;
955  }
956  else if (expression.RightOperand is StringExpression)
957  {
958  key = (string)ValueHelper.Unwrap(InterpretStringExpression(expression.RightOperand as StringExpression));
959  }
960  else if (expression.RightOperand is DynamicMemberExpression)
961  {
962  var memberExp = expression.RightOperand as DynamicMemberExpression;
963  key = ValueHelper.Unwrap(InterpretExpression(memberExp.MemberExpression)).ToString();
964  }
965  else
966  {
967  throw CreateRuntimeException("Unexpected expression {0}", expression.RightOperand);
968  }
969 
970  if (returnRef)
971  {
972  return new AphidRef() { Name = key, Object = obj };
973  }
974  else
975  {
976  AphidObject val;
977 
978  if (obj == null || (obj.Count == 0 && obj.Value == null))
979  {
980  if (expression.LeftOperand.Type != AphidExpressionType.IdentifierExpression)
981  {
982  throw CreateRuntimeException("Null reference exception: {0}", expression);
983  }
984 
985  return InterpretMemberInteropExpression(null, expression, returnRef);
986  }
987  else if (obj.Count == 0)
988  {
989  var aphidType = obj.IsAphidType();
990 
991  val = TypeExtender.TryResolve(
992  CurrentScope,
993  obj,
994  key,
995  isAphidType: aphidType,
996  isCtor: false,
997  isDynamic: false,
998  returnRef: returnRef) ??
999  InterpretMemberInteropExpression(
1000  obj.Value,
1001  expression,
1002  returnRef,
1003  () => TypeExtender.TryResolve(
1004  CurrentScope,
1005  obj,
1006  key,
1007  isAphidType: aphidType,
1008  isCtor: false,
1009  isDynamic: true,
1010  returnRef: returnRef));
1011 
1012  if (val == null)
1013  {
1014  throw CreateException(key, obj, expression);
1015  }
1016 
1017  return val;
1018  }
1019  else if (!obj.TryResolve(key, out val))
1020  {
1021  if (obj.Value != null)
1022  {
1023  val = TypeExtender.TryResolve(
1024  CurrentScope,
1025  obj,
1026  key,
1027  isAphidType: true,
1028  isCtor: false,
1029  isDynamic: false,
1030  returnRef: returnRef);
1031 
1032  return val == null ?
1033  InterpretMemberInteropExpression(
1034  obj.Value,
1035  expression,
1036  returnRef,
1037  () => TypeExtender.TryResolve(
1038  CurrentScope,
1039  obj,
1040  key,
1041  isAphidType: true,
1042  isCtor: false,
1043  isDynamic: true,
1044  returnRef: returnRef)) :
1045  val;
1046  }
1047  else
1048  {
1049  throw CreateException(key, obj, expression);
1050  }
1051  }
1052 
1053  return val;
1054  }
1055  }

1060  return CreateRuntimeException(

1087  [TargetedPatchingOptOut("Performance critical to inline across NGen image boundaries"), MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)]
1088  private object InterpretAssignmentExpression(
1089  AphidExpression destinationExpression,
1090  object value,
1091  bool returnRef = false,
1092  AphidExpression completeExpression = null)
1093  {
1094  //var value = InterpretExpression(expression.RightOperand);
1095  var value2 = ValueHelper.Wrap(value);
1096  AphidFunction func;
1097 
1098  if (destinationExpression.Type == AphidExpressionType.IdentifierExpression)
1099  {
1100  var idExp = (IdentifierExpression)destinationExpression;
1101  var id = idExp.Identifier;
1102 
1103  if (idExp.Attributes.Count == 0 ||
1104  idExp.Attributes[0].Identifier != AphidName.Var)
1105  {
1106  var destObj = InterpretIdentifierExpression(idExp, canResolveType: false);
1107 
1108  if (destObj == null)
1109  {
1110  if (!StrictMode)
1111  {
1112  CurrentScope.Add(id, value2);
1113  }
1114  else
1115  {
1116  throw CreateStrictModeException(id);
1117  }
1118  }
1119  else
1120  {
1121  var parent = CurrentScope.TryResolveParent(id);
1122  parent[id] = value2;
1123  }
1124  }
1125  else
1126  {
1127  if (!CurrentScope.ContainsKey(id))
1128  {
1129  if (ValueHelper.IsComplexAphidObject(value2))
1130  {
1131  CurrentScope.Add(id, value2);
1132  }
1133  else
1134  {
1135  CurrentScope.Add(id, new AphidObject(value2.Value));
1136  }
1137  }
1138  else
1139  {
1140  throw CreateRuntimeException(
1141  "Variable '{0}' has already been defined in the current scope.",
1142  id);
1143  }
1144  }
1145 
1146  return value2;
1147  }
1148  else if (destinationExpression.Type == AphidExpressionType.ArrayAccessExpression)
1149  {
1150  var arrayAccessExp = (ArrayAccessExpression)destinationExpression;
1151  var targetObj = InterpretExpression(arrayAccessExp.ArrayExpression);
1152  var targetObjUnwrapped = ValueHelper.Unwrap(targetObj);
1153 
1154  var keyObjects = new object[arrayAccessExp.KeyExpressions.Count];
1155 
1156  for (var i = 0; i < keyObjects.Length; i++)
1157  {
1158  keyObjects[i] = ValueHelper.Unwrap(
1159  InterpretExpression(arrayAccessExp.KeyExpressions[i]));
1160  }
1161 
1162  if (keyObjects.Length != 1)
1163  {
1164  throw CreateRuntimeException("Multi-dimensional arrays not yet supported.");
1165  }
1166 
1167  var keyObj = keyObjects[0];
1168 
1169  Array targetArray;
1170  List<AphidObject> targetAphidList;
1171 
1172  if ((targetArray = targetObjUnwrapped as Array) != null)
1173  {
1174  targetArray.SetValue(
1175  Convert.ChangeType(
1176  value2.Value,
1177  targetArray.GetType().GetElementType()),
1178  Convert.ToInt32(keyObj));
1179  }
1180  else if ((targetAphidList = targetObjUnwrapped as List<AphidObject>) != null)
1181  {
1182  if (value2.Count == 0 && value2.Value != null)
1183  {
1184  value = value2 = new AphidObject(value2.Value);
1185  }
1186 
1187  targetAphidList[Convert.ToInt32(keyObj)] = value2;
1188  }
1189  else
1190  {
1191  var targetType = targetObjUnwrapped.GetType();
1192 
1193  if (targetType
1194  .GetInterfaces()
1195  .Any(x => x.GetGenericTypeDefinition() == typeof(IList<>)))
1196  {
1197  var index = targetType
1198  .GetProperties()
1199  .Select(x => new { Property = x, Params = x.GetIndexParameters() })
1200  .Single(x =>
1201  x.Params.Length == 1 &&
1202  x.Params[0].ParameterType == typeof(int));
1203 
1204  index.Property.SetValue(
1205  targetObjUnwrapped,
1206  Convert.ChangeType(
1207  value2.Value,
1208  index.Property.PropertyType),
1209  new object[] { Convert.ToInt32(keyObj) });
1210  }
1211  else
1212  {
1213  throw CreateRuntimeException("Could not set value by index.");
1214  }
1215  }
1216  }
1217  else if (destinationExpression.Type == AphidExpressionType.BinaryOperatorExpression)
1218  {
1219  var obj = InterpretBinaryOperatorExpression(
1220  (BinaryOperatorExpression)destinationExpression,
1221  true);
1222 
1223  var objRef = obj as AphidRef;
1224 
1225  if (objRef != null)
1226  {
1227  if (objRef.Object == null)
1228  {
1229  throw CreateRuntimeException("Undefined variable {0}", destinationExpression);
1230  }
1231  else if (objRef.Object.ContainsKey(objRef.Name))
1232  {
1233  if (ValueHelper.IsComplexAphidObject(value))
1234  {
1235  var v = (AphidObject)value;
1236 
1237  if ((func = value2.Value as AphidFunction) != null)
1238  {
1239  func.ParentScope = v;
1240  }
1241 
1242  objRef.Object[objRef.Name] = v;
1243  }
1244  else
1245  {
1246  if ((func = value2.Value as AphidFunction) != null)
1247  {
1248  func.ParentScope = objRef.Object;
1249  }
1250 
1251  //objRef.Object[objRef.Name] = new AphidObject(ValueHelper.Unwrap(value));
1252  objRef.Object[objRef.Name].Value = value2.Value;
1253  }
1254  }
1255  else
1256  {
1257  if (ValueHelper.IsComplexAphidObject(value))
1258  {
1259  objRef.Object.Add(objRef.Name, value2);
1260  }
1261  else
1262  {
1263  objRef.Object.Add(objRef.Name, new AphidObject(value2.Value));
1264  }
1265 
1266  if ((func = value2.Value as AphidFunction) != null)
1267  {
1268  func.ParentScope = objRef.Object;
1269  }
1270  }
1271 
1272  return value;
1273  }
1274 
1275  var interopRef = ValueHelper.Unwrap(obj) as AphidInteropReference;
1276 
1277  if (interopRef == null)
1278  {
1279  obj = InterpretMemberInteropExpression(
1280  null,
1281  (BinaryOperatorExpression)destinationExpression,
1282  returnRef: true);
1283 
1284  interopRef = ValueHelper.Unwrap(obj) as AphidInteropReference;
1285  }
1286 
1287  if (interopRef != null)
1288  {
1289  var v = value2.Value;
1290 
1291  if (interopRef.Field != null)
1292  {
1293  interopRef.Field.SetValue(
1294  interopRef.Object,
1295  TypeConverter.Convert(interopRef.Field.FieldType, v, null));
1296  }
1297  else
1298  {
1299  interopRef.Property.SetValue(
1300  interopRef.Object,
1301  v != null ?
1302  TypeConverter.Convert(interopRef.Property.PropertyType, v, null) :
1303  null);
1304  }
1305 
1306  if ((func = value2.Value as AphidFunction) != null)
1307  {
1308  var o = interopRef.Object;
1309 
1310  var ao = o as AphidObject;
1311 
1312  if (ao != null)
1313  {
1314  func.ParentScope = ao;
1315  }
1316  else
1317  {
1318  func.ParentScope = new AphidObject(o, CurrentScope);
1319  }
1320  }
1321 
1322  return value;
1323  }
1324 
1325 
1326  }
1327  else
1328  {
1329  throw CreateRuntimeException(
1330  "Invalid left hand side of assignment expression: {0}",
1331  completeExpression ?? destinationExpression);
1332  }
1333 
1334  return value;
1335  }

1401  [TargetedPatchingOptOut("Performance critical to inline across NGen image boundaries"), MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)]
1402  private object InterpretBinaryOperatorExpression(BinaryOperatorExpression expression, bool returnRef = false)
1403  {
1404  switch (expression.Operator)
1405  {
1406  case AphidTokenType.AdditionOperator:
1407  return OperatorHelper.Add(
1408  InterpretExpression(expression.LeftOperand) as AphidObject,
1409  InterpretExpression(expression.RightOperand) as AphidObject);
1410 
1411  case AphidTokenType.MinusOperator:
1412  return OperatorHelper.Subtract(
1413  InterpretExpression(expression.LeftOperand) as AphidObject,
1414  InterpretExpression(expression.RightOperand) as AphidObject);
1415 
1416  case AphidTokenType.MultiplicationOperator:
1417  return OperatorHelper.Multiply(
1418  InterpretExpression(expression.LeftOperand) as AphidObject,
1419  InterpretExpression(expression.RightOperand) as AphidObject);
1420 
1421  case AphidTokenType.DivisionOperator:
1422  return OperatorHelper.Divide(
1423  InterpretExpression(expression.LeftOperand) as AphidObject,
1424  InterpretExpression(expression.RightOperand) as AphidObject);
1425 
1426  case AphidTokenType.MemberOperator:
1427  return InterpretMemberExpression(expression, returnRef);
1428 
1429  case AphidTokenType.AssignmentOperator:
1430  return InterpretAssignmentExpression(expression, returnRef);
1431 
1432  case AphidTokenType.PlusEqualOperator:
1433  return InterprentOperatorAndAssignmentExpression(OperatorHelper.Add, expression);
1434 
1435  case AphidTokenType.MinusEqualOperator:
1436  return InterprentOperatorAndAssignmentExpression(OperatorHelper.Subtract, expression);
1437 
1438  case AphidTokenType.MultiplicationEqualOperator:
1439  return InterprentOperatorAndAssignmentExpression(OperatorHelper.Multiply, expression);
1440 
1441  case AphidTokenType.DivisionEqualOperator:
1442  return InterprentOperatorAndAssignmentExpression(OperatorHelper.Divide, expression);
1443 
1444  case AphidTokenType.ModulusEqualOperator:
1445  return InterprentOperatorAndAssignmentExpression(OperatorHelper.Mod, expression);
1446 
1447  case AphidTokenType.BinaryAndEqualOperator:
1448  return InterprentOperatorAndAssignmentExpression(OperatorHelper.BinaryAnd, expression);
1449 
1450  case AphidTokenType.OrEqualOperator:
1451  return InterprentOperatorAndAssignmentExpression(OperatorHelper.BinaryOr, expression);
1452 
1453  case AphidTokenType.XorEqualOperator:
1454  return InterprentOperatorAndAssignmentExpression(OperatorHelper.Xor, expression);
1455 
1456  case AphidTokenType.ShiftLeftEqualOperator:
1457  return InterprentOperatorAndAssignmentExpression(OperatorHelper.BinaryShiftLeft, expression);
1458 
1459  case AphidTokenType.ShiftRightEqualOperator:
1460  return InterprentOperatorAndAssignmentExpression(OperatorHelper.BinaryShiftRight, expression);
1461 
1462  case AphidTokenType.NotEqualOperator:
1463  case AphidTokenType.EqualityOperator:
1464  return InterpretEqualityExpression(expression);
1465 
1466  case AphidTokenType.LessThanOperator:
1467  return CompareDecimals(expression, (x, y) => x < y);
1468 
1469  case AphidTokenType.LessThanOrEqualOperator:
1470  return CompareDecimals(expression, (x, y) => x <= y);
1471 
1472  case AphidTokenType.GreaterThanOperator:
1473  return CompareDecimals(expression, (x, y) => x > y);
1474 
1475  case AphidTokenType.GreaterThanOrEqualOperator:
1476  return CompareDecimals(expression, (x, y) => x >= y);
1477 
1478  case AphidTokenType.AndOperator:
1479  return InterpretAndExpression(expression);
1480 
1481  case AphidTokenType.OrOperator:
1482  return InterpretOrExpression(expression);
1483 
1484  case AphidTokenType.ModulusOperator:
1485  return OperatorHelper.Mod(
1486  InterpretExpression(expression.LeftOperand) as AphidObject,
1487  InterpretExpression(expression.RightOperand) as AphidObject);
1488 
1489  case AphidTokenType.ShiftLeft:
1490  return OperatorHelper.BinaryShiftLeft(
1491  InterpretExpression(expression.LeftOperand) as AphidObject,
1492  InterpretExpression(expression.RightOperand) as AphidObject);
1493 
1494  case AphidTokenType.ShiftRight:
1495  return OperatorHelper.BinaryShiftRight(
1496  InterpretExpression(expression.LeftOperand) as AphidObject,
1497  InterpretExpression(expression.RightOperand) as AphidObject);
1498 
1499  case AphidTokenType.BinaryAndOperator:

1550  expression.RightOperand,

1555 
1556

1564  expression,
1565  expression.RightOperand,
1566  func,
1567  new[] { x, y })));

1571

1575  InterpretFunctionExpression(
1576  expression,
1577  expression.RightOperand,
1578  func,

1587  InterpretFunctionExpression(

1589  expression.RightOperand,

1937  [TargetedPatchingOptOut("Performance critical to inline across NGen image boundaries"), MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)]
1938  private AphidObject InterpretBinaryOperatorBodyExpression(BinaryOperatorBodyExpression expression)
1939  {
1940  var key = GetCustomOperatorKey(expression.Operator);
1941  var key2 = GetCustomOperatorExpressionKey(expression.Operator);
1942  var func = InterpretFunctionExpression(expression.Function);
1943 
1944  AphidObject obj, obj2;
1945 
1946  if (CurrentScope.TryGetValue(key, out obj))
1947  {
1948  obj.Value = func.GetFunction();
1949  CurrentScope.TryGetValue(key2, out obj2);
1950  obj2.Value = expression;
1951 
1952  return obj;
1953  }
1954  else
1955  {
1956  CurrentScope.Add(key, func);
1957  CurrentScope.Add(key2, new AphidObject(expression));
1958 
1959  return func;
1960  }
1961  }

1963  [TargetedPatchingOptOut("Performance critical to inline across NGen image boundaries"), MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)]
1964  private AphidObject InterpretFunctionComposition(BinaryOperatorExpression composition)
1965  {
1966  var funcs = new[] { composition.LeftOperand, composition.RightOperand }
1967  .Select(x => ValueHelper.Unwrap(InterpretExpression(x)))
1968  .ToArray();
1969 
1970  var c = new AphidFunctionComposition(
1971  composition.LeftOperand,
1972  composition.RightOperand,
1973  funcs[0],
1974  funcs[1]);
1975 
1976  return new AphidObject(c);
1977  }

2003  [TargetedPatchingOptOut("Performance critical to inline across NGen image boundaries"), MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)]
2004  private AphidObject CallCustomOperatorFunction(
2005  AphidExpression customOperatorExpression,
2006  AphidTokenType op,
2007  string name,
2008  object[] args)
2009  {
2010  var funcName = GetCustomOperatorFunction(op, name);
2011  var funcExp = CurrentScope.Resolve(this, GetCustomOperatorExpressionKey(op));
2012  PushFrame(customOperatorExpression, (AphidExpression)funcExp.Value, args);
2013 
2014  try
2015  {
2016  return CallFunction(funcName, args);
2017  }
2018  finally
2019  {
2020  PopFrame();
2021  }
2022  }

2024  [TargetedPatchingOptOut("Performance critical to inline across NGen image boundaries"), MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)]
2025  private AphidFunction GetCustomOperatorFunction(AphidTokenType op, string name)
2026  {
2027  AphidObject obj;
2028 
2029  if (!CurrentScope.TryResolve(GetCustomOperatorKey(op), out obj))
2030  {
2031  throw CreateRuntimeException("Custom operator '{0}' not defined.", op);
2032  }
2033 
2034  var func = obj.GetFunction();
2035 
2036  if (func == null)
2037  {
2038  throw CreateRuntimeException(
2039  "Custom operator '{0}' should be function, was '{1}'.",
2040  op,
2041  obj.GetValueType());
2042  }
2043 
2044  return func;
2045  }

2065  try

2868  [TargetedPatchingOptOut("Performance critical to inline across NGen image boundaries"), MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)]
2869  private AphidObject InterpretInteropNewExpression(AphidExpression operand)
2870  {
2871  switch (operand.Type)
2872  {
2873  case AphidExpressionType.CallExpression:
2874  var call = operand.ToCall();
2875 
2876  var args = call.Args
2877  .Select(InterpretExpression)
2878  .Select(ValueHelper.DeepUnwrap)
2879  .ToArray();
2880 
2881  PushFrame(operand, operand, args);
2882 
2883  try
2884  {
2885  var typeObj = ValueHelper.Unwrap(InterpretExpression(call.FunctionExpression));
2886 
2887  if (typeObj == null || !typeof(Type).IsAssignableFrom(typeObj.GetType()))
2888  {
2889  throw CreateRuntimeException(
2890  "Expression '{0}' resolved to '{1}', expected type.",
2891  call.FunctionExpression,
2892  typeObj);
2893  }
2894 
2895  var type = (Type)typeObj;
2896  var ctor = InteropMethodResolver.Resolve(type.GetConstructors(), args);
2897 
2898  var convertedArgs = TypeConverter.Convert(
2899  ctor.Arguments,
2900  ctor.GenericArguments);
2901 
2902  var result = ((ConstructorInfo)ctor.Method).Invoke(convertedArgs);
2903  var obj = ValueHelper.Wrap(result);
2904 
2905  var extension = TypeExtender.TryResolve(
2906  CurrentScope,
2907  obj,
2908  TypeExtender.GetCtorName(type.FullName),
2909  false,
2910  isCtor: true,
2911  isDynamic: false,
2912  returnRef: false);
2913 
2914  if (extension != null)
2915  {
2916  var func = extension.Value as AphidFunction;
2917 
2918  if (func != null)
2919  {
2920  var obj2 = CallFunction(func, obj);
2921 
2922  if (obj2 != null)
2923  {
2924  obj = obj2;
2925  }
2926  }
2927  else
2928  {
2929  obj = extension;
2930  }
2931  }
2932 
2933  return obj;
2934  }
2935  finally
2936  {
2937  PopFrame();
2938  }
2939 
2940  default:
2941  throw CreateRuntimeException("Operand not supported in new expression: {0}", operand);
2942  }
2943  }

2957  [TargetedPatchingOptOut("Performance critical to inline across NGen image boundaries"), MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)]
2958  private AphidObject InterpretArrayExpression(ArrayExpression expression)

2979  [TargetedPatchingOptOut("Performance critical to inline across NGen image boundaries"), MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)]
2980  private AphidObject InterpretUnaryOperatorExpression(UnaryOperatorExpression expression)
2981  {
2982  if (!expression.IsPostfix)
2983  {
2984  switch (expression.Operator)
2985  {
2986  case AphidTokenType.AdditionOperator:
2987  return (AphidObject)InterpretExpression(expression.Operand);
2988 
2989  case AphidTokenType.MinusOperator:
2990  var val = ValueHelper.Unwrap(InterpretExpression(expression.Operand));
2991 
2992  if (!(val is decimal))
2993  {
2994  throw CreateRuntimeException(
2995  "Unary operator '-' expects number, {0} was provided instead.",
2996  val.GetType());
2997  }
2998 
2999  return ValueHelper.Wrap((decimal)val * -1);
3000 
3001  case AphidTokenType.ComplementOperator:
3002  val = InterpretAndUnwrap(expression.Operand);
3003  ValueHelper.AssertNumber(val, "unary operator '~'");
3004 
3005  return ValueHelper.Wrap((decimal)~Convert.ToUInt64(val));
3006 
3007  case AphidTokenType.retKeyword:
3008  SetReturnValue(ValueHelper.Wrap(InterpretExpression(expression.Operand)));
3009  _isReturning = true;
3010  return null;
3011 
3012  case AphidTokenType.deleteKeyword:
3013  var operand = ((IdentifierExpression)expression.Operand).Identifier;
3014  return new AphidObject(CurrentScope.TryResolveAndRemove(operand));
3015 
3016  case AphidTokenType.NotOperator:
3017  return new AphidObject(!(bool)ValueHelper.Unwrap(InterpretExpression(expression.Operand) as AphidObject));
3018 
3019  case AphidTokenType.IncrementOperator:
3020  var obj = InterpretExpression(expression.Operand) as AphidObject;
3021  obj.Value = ((decimal)obj.Value) + 1;
3022  return obj;
3023 
3024  case AphidTokenType.DecrementOperator:
3025  obj = InterpretExpression(expression.Operand) as AphidObject;
3026  obj.Value = ((decimal)obj.Value) - 1;
3027  return obj;
3028 
3029  case AphidTokenType.DistinctOperator:
3030  var opExp = InterpretExpression(expression.Operand);
3031  var list = ((IEnumerable<object>)ValueHelper.UnwrapAndBoxCollection(opExp));
3032 
3033  var result = list
3034  .Select(ValueHelper.Unwrap)
3035  .Distinct()
3036  .Select(ValueHelper.Wrap) // To maintain backwards compat with Aphid
3037  .ToList(); // list extension such as __list.count().
3038 
3039  return ValueHelper.Wrap(result);
3040 
3041  //return new AphidObject(list.Distinct(_comparer).ToList());
3042 
3043  case AphidTokenType.usingKeyword:
3044  var path = FlattenAndJoinPath(expression.Operand);
3045  AddImport(path);
3046 
3047  return null;
3048 
3049  case AphidTokenType.newKeyword:
3050  return InterpretInteropNewExpression(expression.Operand);
3051 
3052  case AphidTokenType.loadKeyword:
3053  // Todo: make more robust by searching application dir,
3054  // script dir, etc.
3055  Assembly asm = null;
3056 
3057  switch (expression.Operand.Type)
3058  {
3059  case AphidExpressionType.IdentifierExpression:
3060  case AphidExpressionType.BinaryOperatorExpression:
3061  path = FlattenAndJoinPath(expression.Operand);
3062  asm = Assembly.LoadWithPartialName(path);
3063  break;
3064 
3065  case AphidExpressionType.StringExpression:
3066  var strExp = (StringExpression)expression.Operand;
3067  var str = StringParser.Parse(strExp.Value);
3068 
3069  if (File.Exists(path = Path.GetFullPath(str)))
3070  {
3071  asm = Assembly.LoadFile(path);
3072  }
3073 
3074  break;
3075  }
3076 
3077  if (asm == null)
3078  {
3079  // Todo: safely deref member expression to avoid
3080  // null ref exception on fallback.
3081  var loadOperand = InterpretExpression(expression.Operand);
3082  var unwrappedPath = ValueHelper.Unwrap(loadOperand);
3083 
3084  if (unwrappedPath == null)
3085  {
3086  return new AphidObject(null);
3087  }
3088 
3089  if (File.Exists(path = unwrappedPath.ToString()))
3090  {
3091  asm = Assembly.LoadFile(path);
3092  }
3093  }
3094 
3095  return new AphidObject(asm);
3096 
3097  case AphidTokenType.InteropOperator:
3098  var attr = GetInteropAttribute(expression.Operand);
3099 
3100  switch (attr)
3101  {
3102  case null:
3103  switch (expression.Operand.Type)
3104  {
3105  case AphidExpressionType.CallExpression:
3106  var callExp = (CallExpression)expression.Operand;
3107  return CallStaticInteropFunction(callExp);
3108 
3109  case AphidExpressionType.BinaryOperatorExpression:
3110  return InterpretMemberInteropExpression(
3111  null,
3112  expression.Operand.ToBinaryOperator());
3113 
3114  default:
3115  throw new NotImplementedException();
3116  }
3117 
3118  default:
3119  throw new NotImplementedException();
3120 
3121  }

4617  private void Interpret(List<AphidExpression> expressions, bool resetIsReturning = true)
4618  {

4620  {
4621  OnInterpretBlockExecuting = true;
4622

4635  return;

4639  {
4640  OnInterpretBlockExecuting = false;

4654  _insertNextBuffer = null;
